#: app/Strings.php:104
msgid "Choose where you want to show the tab"
msgstr "Choisissez où afficher l’onglet."

#: app/Strings.php:105
msgid "The tabs will be shown first and the table will be shown after it"
msgstr "Les onglets seront affichés en premier, puis le tableau."

